OOC: Hot Rod is in a CR, at the Alliance base.

::Hot Rod::

He woke up. He didn't know how, but he had the since that something bad
had happaned to Feline. Something fatel. He got out of the CR, out of
the ship, and headed back to the battle. He hoped she was ok. Things
were going good between them. Hot Rod never had things good with femms.
He had loved the Autobot femmm ArrCee, but she left him for Springer. He
had feelings for the Maximal Savanna, but she was killed. He also had
fellings for Kamodia, but he gave them up because ArcAngel liked her.
Feline seemed to be the one.
